    .participate#get-involved
      .participate__wrapper
        .participate__headline How can I&nbsp;get&nbsp;involved?
        .participate__subline 
          p Activist, dreamer, do-er? 
          p Excited, angry, frustrated? 
          p Developer, talker, tester?
        .participate__text.participate__text--align-bottom We are always looking for enthusiastic people to join our international team. No matter where you are in the world, if you can commit four hours a week we can do with your help.

      .participate__wrapper
        .participate__subline Current roles we are looking for:
        ul.participate__roles
          li <em>BETA users</em> (gain exclusive first access to the latest features and tools and provide valuable feedback to help set our strategy)
          li <em>UX researcher</em> (Europe based)
          li <em>data analyst/engineer</em> (SQL required, Python and Google Analytics are a plus)
          li <em>DevOps engineer</em> (Azure, CI/CD)
          li <em>mid-level / senior full stack developer</em>
          li <em>mid-level / senior backend developer</em> (Python)
          li <em>mid-level / senior frontend developer</em> (React, Typescript)
          li <em>web content curator</em> (knowledgeable about climate change or eager to research and summarize reading)
          li <em>web content editor/writer</em> (good at summarizing and shortening text to be clear and appealing)
          li <em>web content reviewer</em> (copyeditor)

        .participate__text Have you got the skills we are looking for and are you motivated to take action? Then get in touch with us and we will send you more details about how you can join our team.
        .participate__cta
